com.sun.identity.plugin.monitoring

Interface FedMonIDFFSvc

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    FedletMonIDFFSvcProvider, FedMonIDFFSvcProvider

    public interface FedMonIDFFSvc
    This interface defines methods which will be invoked by the Federation Framework to update monitoring-related counters
